{"tid":2040097,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《反送中裡的性暴力》懶人包","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T10:59:52.000Z","uid":359469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e319311df96caf2a751569db1578dafc1effe0a","tid":2040097,"uid":359469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"大家好，我是國立臺灣大學社會系的學生，最近一年香港的局勢，我和同學們都非常關注，也觀察到在整起香港反送中運動中，有許多性暴力事件的發生。這幾天也看到香港警察再次展開無差別濫捕，連放學的中學女生都被押進警車，我們非常關切這個事件的發展走向，因為民主自由是我們共同相信的價值。我們製作了一個懶人包，裡面討論了警察如何透過國家威權對女性進行支配，以及陽剛文化的霸權，若大家有任何想法也歡迎在底下留言、討論，有需要也歡迎轉載，謝謝大家。願香港平安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7oz7Ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7oz7Ca.png&h=eab1b19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0mmNCd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0mmNCd.png&h=13a131c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rc5R9QA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frc5R9QA.png&h=28bb66fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2UrYJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2UrYJY.png&h=67883352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oF5uWvG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoF5uWvG.png&h=17d49a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kvbub34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKvbub34.png&h=b486aa78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJ1quQK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJ1quQK.png&h=3ce40928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0CpLo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0CpLo6.png&h=a51bc788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONfR9QN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c